<lb ed="B" n="0321b10"/><note place="inline">貳房</note></p></cb:div><cb:div type="other"><cb:mulu type="其他" level="3">基址伍畆</cb:mulu><p xml:id="pB29p0321b1003" style="margin-left:2em" cb:place="inline">基址伍畆<note place="inline">東至安德街　南至能仁寺墻　西至璢璃窑水塘　北至官路</note></p></cb:div></cb:div></cb:div>
